    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with Medium model influence. Validation error (max RH 9.3%) is within the ±15% acceptance band. The UQ campaign documented in VR-CPB-2024-07 Appendix D confirms that RH rankings are robust to geometric parameter variation across the design space, supporting the conclusion that the CFD model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The model is accepted for the stated COU.",
